.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH oxiarc-convert 1  "oxiarc-convert " 
.SH NAME
oxiarc\-convert \- Convert archive to another format
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBoxiarc\-convert\fR [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-l\fR|\fB\-\-compression\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIINPUT\fR> <\fIOUTPUT\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Convert archive to another format
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR
Output format (zip, tar, gzip, lzh, xz, lz4, br, snappy) \- auto\-detected from extension if not specified
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
zip: ZIP archive
.IP \(bu 2
tar: TAR archive
.IP \(bu 2
gzip: GZIP compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
lzh: LZH archive
.IP \(bu 2
xz: XZ compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
lz4: LZ4 compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
bz2: Bzip2 compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
zst: Zstandard compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
br: Brotli compressed file
.IP \(bu 2
snappy: Snappy compressed file
.RE
.TP
\fB\-l\fR, \fB\-\-compression\fR \fI<COMPRESSION>\fR [default: normal]
Compression level for output
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
store: Store without compression
.IP \(bu 2
fast: Fast compression
.IP \(bu 2
normal: Normal compression (default)
.IP \(bu 2
best: Best compression
.RE
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Verbose output
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
<\fIINPUT\fR>
Input archive file
.TP
<\fIOUTPUT\fR>
Output archive file
